    <title>Attention or Sentiment: How Social Media React to ESG?</title>
    <updated>2025-10-15T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Xiaoquan (Michael) Zhang, DaPeng Xu, Hong Hong, Kalok Chan</name>
