    <title>EXPRESS: AI and Immunity to the COVID-19 Pandemic</title>
    <updated>2025-10-21T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Abhishek Bhatia, Nikhil Madan, Deepa Mani, Shekhar Tomar</name>
